    "Update the workflow state so it stores `digest : LeadFollowUpDigest`.",
    "Update the lead summary API route so it returns `LeadFollowUpDigest`.",
    "Keep the program compiling.",
    "Keep `main` working. After the change, `main` should evaluate to `\"sales-manager\"`."
  ],
  "fileHints": [
    "Main.clasp",
    "Shared/Lead.clasp"
  ],
  "oracleHints": [
